---
title: Double Chermoula-Spiced Chicken & Veggie Medley with Garlic Yoghurt & Toasted Almonds
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve enlisted the help of our lively Middle Eastern-inspired chermoula spice blend: it coats each bite of tender chicken breast in vibrant, earthy flavours and pairs perfectly with the robust roast veggie medley. Go for your life!

